Package de.oth.blocklib.threading

Class CompletableFutureWrapper

java.lang.Object
de.oth.blocklib.threading.CompletableFutureWrapper
class CompletableFutureWrapper
extends java.lang.Object
The type Completable future wrapper. Uses the decorator pattern to wrap tasks in CompletingCallable objects and return CompletableFuture or ScheduledCompletableFuture objects that can be used to compose jobs.
Author:
Loher Florian
